OL,5,Ctree
OL,7,FMr Hayward, trading as G H Hayward
OL,8,FForestry Contractors, had been making
OL,9,Fa back cut to the tree when it fell in
OL,10,Fthe wrong direction.
OL,12,FIt then landed on the injured worker,
OL,13,Fwho was standing in a nearby bridle
OL,14,Fpath.
OL,16,FThe worker, from Frome, sustained
OL,17,Feight broken ribs, a broken pelvis,
OL,18,Ftwo broken ankles, a collapsed lung
OL,19,Fand internal bleeding.
