OL,4,Cworker, 61, left paralysed by falling
OL,5,Ctree
OL,7,FHe was placed in an induced coma for
OL,8,Ftwo weeks and later spent four months
OL,9,Fin hospital.
OL,11,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,12,FSafety Executive (HSE) found Mr
OL,13,FHayward, who was in charge of the tree
OL,14,Ffelling, failed to implement a safe
OL,15,Fworking zone around the tree as it was
OL,16,Fbeing felled.
OL,18,FA safe working zone is usually twice
OL,19,Fthe size of the tree, with only the
OL,20,Ffelling operator permitted inside the
OL,21,Fzone.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
