OL,4,Cworker, 61, left paralysed by falling
OL,5,Ctree
OL,7,FThe tree fell in the unintended
OL,8,Fdirection as the cut made by Mr
OL,9,FHayward did not leave a functioning
OL,10,Fhinge.
OL,12,FGerald Hayward, of Blandford Forum,
OL,13,Fpleaded guilty to breaching Section
OL,14,F3(2) of the Health and Safety at Work
OL,15,Fetc. Act 1974.
OL,17,FHe was fined #1,000 and ordered to pay
OL,18,F#1,000 in costs at Salisbury
OL,19,FMagistrates' Court on 15 October 2024.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
