OL,5,Ctree
OL,7,FHSE inspector James Hole said: "This
OL,8,Fwas a serious incident that has led to
OL,9,Fan individual sustaining life-changing
OL,10,Finjuries meaning he is now unable to
OL,11,Fwork and requires lifelong care.
OL,13,F"Mr Hayward failed to create a safe
OL,14,Fworking zone around the tree while it
OL,15,Fwas being cut down ` this is a
OL,16,Fstandard working practice for tree
OL,17,Ffelling in woodland.
OL,19,F"He failed to implement the correct
OL,20,Fcontrol measures and a safe system of
OL,21,Fwork.
